    <note>Li(2) Hu(2) [20577] Li(2) Bian's [19629] son, Min [20571], younger brother of Jing [3485], moved to Huaixi circuit when Li(2) Yu [3551], last ruler of Southern Tang, returned to allegiance. Min's grandson, Zhongxuan [20573] #4 and youngest son of Duo(2) [20572], accompanied his unnamed elder brother, who had been appointed Shucheng county magistrate. Zhongxuan bought land and settled in the area. Zhongxuan's grandson, Xuyi [20575], was Hu(2)'s great grandfather. Zhou Bida, WJ, 78.4a-7b. CBD, 2, 879.</note>
